{"type": "article", "id": 3545, "title": "Cambium 充电底座", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-14T08:18:40Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232956sdQGSXqR3MtDZmb2.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t</p>\n<p>\r\n\t\t来自爱丁堡的设计公司 Namisu 日前推出一款名为「Cambium」的充电底座。设计团队将底座的钢材与表面的白蜡木材质两种元素融合，制作了一款造型极为简洁的圆形充电底座。此外，这款充电底座内部还配有一条可以伸缩收纳的充电电线，取代了传统裸露在外部的传统充电线，更显干净利落。Namisu 认为，使用苹果产品是一种很好的体验，那么伴随它的配件也理应给予用户相同的体验。目前，Cambium 正在<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/54235873/cambium-minimal-dock\" target=\"_blank\"> Kickstarter </a>上进行众筹，预计出货时间为明年 3 月。\r\n\t</p>\r\n\t<p>\r\n\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052329548bePiNazl7TQogKH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232954mXJBerGO1anEkMKQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232955BrAvpmX3LhIM5xib.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052329559nT4SHKvqjJfPUlr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232955YPVgnrIWCBwm89Ai.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t</p>\r\n\n\n"}